title: WVU to make fifth-straight Robo-Ops Challenge appearance (West Virginia University)
text: ( Source : West Virginia University ) Students from West Virginia University will once again get to show off their robot-building skills when they make their fifth straight appearance at the Revolutionary Aerospace Systems Concepts-Academic
